00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:03,840
His uncle looked over at him.

350
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:07,840
"Owen, some things hurt too much to talk about."

351
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,400
"Do you think you could talk about it now?"

